#include <iostream>
using namespace std;

int main(){
    int N;
    long long dp[91][2];
    cin >> N;
    dp[1][0] = 1;
    dp[1][1] = 1;
    for (int i = 2; i <= N; i++) {
        dp[i][0] = dp[i-1][0] + dp[i-1][1];

}
